{"tid":1314292,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對五毛用教戰守則","createTime":"2019-07-14T06:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T06:08:58.000Z","uid":86488,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"af02665f3276c60bd08aa40d875e112d812601ac","tid":1314292,"uid":86488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:08:58.000Z","msg":"本人作為一個歷戰多年既反五毛鍵盤戰士<br />\n對於反五毛呢件事有深刻既體會<br />\n喺長年對抗五毛嘅過程中<br />\n我發現同五毛講嘢用道理係冇用嘅<br />\n同時間我都發現左YT上面有唔少關於維尼嘅meme<br />\n於是我決定利用佢哋對維尼嘅崇拜去對抗呢班人<br />\n以下正式開始教學<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 對話內容要以維尼meme為主</span><br />\n<br />\n所謂嘅維尼meme其實就係維尼語錄<br />\n呢啲語錄由於充滿小學生氣息<br />\n因此亦被不少內地網民恥笑<br />\n內地網站亦都會封鎖相關字詞以保持維尼形象<br />\n<br />\n滿臉噴糞<br />\n輕關易道，通商寬<span style=\"color: red;\">衣</span><br />\n中國<span style=\"color: red;\">人均國內生產總值</span>接近八千萬美元。<br />\n薩格爾王<br />\n金科律玉<br />\n老人瞻仰（<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%AF%B9%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%89%E8%AE%AE#%E5%8F%A3%E8%AF%AF%E4%BA%89%E8%AE%AE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25AF%25B9%25E4%25B9%25A0%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BA%2589%25E8%25AE%25AE%23%25E5%258F%25A3%25E8%25AF%25AF%25E4%25BA%2589%25E8%25AE%25AE&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXParJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=6449321b\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%AF%B9%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%89%E8%AE%AE#%E5%8F%A3%E8%AF%AF%E4%BA%89%E8%AE%AE</a>）<br />\n天行健，君子以<span style=\"color: red;\">不強自&hellip;&hellip;自強不息</span>。<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VD2-9Jjxoes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVD2-9Jjxoes&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXParJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=fa91e0f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VD2-9Jjxoes</a><br />\n冰棒外交 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReturnAbsolute/status/1144806138723983361?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FReturnAbsolute%2Fstatus%2F1144806138723983361%3Fs%3D19&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXParJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=28c0f214\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FReturnAbsolute%2Fstatus%2F1144806138723983361%3Fs%3D19&h=7e0d0758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ReturnAbsolute/status/1144806138723983361?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n二百斤麥子 十里山路不換肩 （<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60076&amp;snA=5098213\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D60076%26snA%3D5098213&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXParJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=d1e9c1f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60076&amp;snA=5098213</a>）<br />\n實際上那些錯誤執行者，他也是有一本賬的，這個賬是記在那兒的。一旦他出事了，這個賬全給你拉出來了。別看你今天鬧得歡，小心今後拉清單，這都得應驗的。不要幹這種事情。<span style=\"color: red;\">頭上三尺有神明</span>，一定要有敬畏之心。（<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6760250&amp;page=1）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6760250%26page%3D1%EF%BC%89&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXParJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=03310259\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6760250&amp;page=1）</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 盡量以表面上支持五毛，實質上諷刺嘅做法令佢哋收聲</span><br />\n<br />\n利用維尼語錄嘅權威性<br />\n加上民族主義嘅思想<br />\n令呢班五毛冇辦法攻擊我哋嘅comment<br />\n達至不戰而勝嘅效果<br />\n如果有人話我哋攻擊維尼講錯野<br />\n我哋可以利用維尼嘅權威令佢哋收聲<br />\n例如「你竟然話維尼會講錯野？」<br />\n從而令佢哋唔敢質疑我哋嘅語錄<br />\np.s.請搭配簡體字使用<br />\n<br />\n有其他心得我會再分享，目前還未遇到處理唔到嘅comment"}]}